You're not toxic to those around you.

32:32.695 --> 32:34.077
You are washed in his blood.

32:36.060 --> 32:37.562
That is what hit me about this.

32:37.622 --> 32:41.788
I thought, how incredible, again, God's fingerprints all over this.

32:43.390 --> 32:48.978
The last point I had here is God calls me to be set apart and washed clean.

32:50.754 --> 32:53.317
He has given you a passion and a purpose.

32:54.018 --> 32:55.280
