32:56.281 --> 32:57.623
He has gifted you with clarity.

32:58.604 --> 33:00.587
He is showing you what you can do with this.

33:01.188 --> 33:04.712
And he's telling you that we should be set apart and washed clean in his blood.

33:04.752 --> 33:09.238
He is calling for you to accept his gift of salvation.

33:09.539 --> 33:11.782
He's calling for you to accept the gift of salvation.

33:12.923 --> 33:13.384
It's there.

33:15.487 --> 33:18.130
Acts 22, 16 says, and now why do you wait?

33:18.466 --> 33:21.669
Rise and be baptized and wash away your sins calling on his name.

33:22.911 --> 33:28.176
Revelation 714 says, and he said to me, these are the ones coming out of the great tribulation.

33:28.536 --> 33:32.120
They have washed their robes and made them white in the blood of the lamb.

33:33.642 --> 33:34.583
That's what he wants us to be.

33:36.825 --> 33:45.554
Can't serve him if you're not supported by him, if you're not in him, if you're not working for him, if you're not devoting your life to him and letting him lead you.

33:46.722 --> 33:47.963
God is calling you to do that.

33:48.003 --> 33:56.371
He's calling you to give you, to give, to accept the gift that he's given you and to accept that salvation and to give your life to him.

33:57.412 --> 33:59.654
And then you can do amazing things.

34:01.416 --> 34:01.956
Have you done that?

34:04.959 --> 34:07.161
