34:15.729 --> 34:16.530
He's gifted you.

34:17.090 --> 34:18.492
and he wants you to work in his kingdom.

34:19.714 --> 34:22.678
If you haven't done that, you can do it today, you can do it now.

34:24.460 --> 34:29.307
You can ask him into your life to lead you and let you be productive for his kingdom.

34:31.951 --> 34:33.272
And all you gotta do is just pray.

34:33.333 --> 34:35.275
As a matter of fact, pray something like this, let's pray.

34:35.936 --> 34:45.970
Father, I pray that if someone is here and they are seeking you and they feel the passion that you've given them, they feel the gift that you have for them or they just

34:46.146 --> 34:47.087
They don't know you yet.

34:47.128 --> 34:48.630
