34:50.152 --> 34:53.617
Lord, I pray that that person says to you that, Lord, I accept your gift.

34:54.559 --> 35:05.135
I know that you died for me to wash me clean, to set me apart in this world, to let me have a tremendous impact for your kingdom, to do amazing things for you.

35:06.177 --> 35:08.861
