35:16.962 --> 35:28.621
And Lord, for everyone else in this room, I just pray that this resonates with their heart, Lord, that they are encouraged to serve, that they take the next step of that service for you, or that they seek the skills.

35:28.681 --> 35:32.788
They really just grow the passion you've given them, fan that into flame.

35:33.690 --> 35:36.354
Lord, that we rely on you fully and wholly in our lives.

35:37.656 --> 35:39.860
We thank you so much for the gifts you've given us.

35:41.923 --> 35:43.025
